WEBVTT

00:00.233 --> 00:01.929
Previously on "The Fix"...

00:01.952 --> 00:04.147
Maya Travis, will you marry me?

00:04.171 --> 00:06.024
I'm not hearing a yes.

00:06.048 --> 00:08.526
- I have to protect this family.
- What is it?

00:08.550 --> 00:10.377
Papers making me a controlling partner

00:10.401 --> 00:11.896
- in your trust.
- What?

00:14.456 --> 00:16.434
He almost died because of you.

00:16.458 --> 00:19.118
All you are to my husband
is political cover.

00:19.142 --> 00:20.138
That's a shadow.

00:20.162 --> 00:22.040
Somebody else was in the storage unit

00:22.064 --> 00:23.942
when Jessica made these tapes.

00:23.966 --> 00:25.443
She was gonna kill me.

00:25.467 --> 00:27.845
Training at a gun range
like a bloody assassin.

00:27.869 --> 00:29.647
You actually might be innocent.

00:29.671 --> 00:31.049
My dad tried to warn me,

00:31.073 --> 00:32.417
and I should have listened.

00:32.441 --> 00:34.585
Wait. I need to say his name.

00:34.609 --> 00:36.477
Let's start over.

